            <div type="section" xml:id="Legislation">
                <head>Legislation</head>
                <p>A 2002 Presidential Decree set up the Committee for Archives and Records
                    Management, but does not legislate a right to access.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Location">
                <head>Location</head>
                <p>Ministry of Foreign Affairs: 19 Lenin St., Minsk 220030, Republic of Belarus</p>
                <p>National Archives: 10 Kollektornaya St., Minsk 220004, Republic of Belarus</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Procedures">
                <head> Procedures</head>
                <p> Researchers should send an official letter of application to the Ministry of
                    Foreign Affairs and the National Archives. </p>
            </div>
